source: TEXT_HEAVNZ725_01929_SEQ_00<tab>Gullinkambi utters a growl, but not from her mouth.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ725_01929_SEQ_00<tab>On pourrait entendre l'estomac de Gullinkambi gargouiller plusieurs malms à la ronde.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ725_01929_SEQ_01<tab>Gullinkambi spends countless moons atop the tower of Anyx Trine guarding her eggs. For lack of time to hunt, she has grown hungry and craves bandersnatch for her next meal. Travel to the cave near the Iron Feast and slay three bandersnatches for their meat.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ725_01929_SEQ_01<tab>Affamée, Gullinkambi vous a demandé de l'aider à se remplir l'estomac. Rendez-vous à proximité des Cent Râles et tuez <var 33 ((BNpcName)) 02F20E040302 /var> pour obtenir trois morceaux de leur viande.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ725_01929_SEQ_02<tab>You slay three bandersnatches and obtain their meat. Deliver the meat to Gullinkambi, that she may satisfy her cravings.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ725_01929_SEQ_02<tab>Vous avez obtenu trois <var 33 ((EventItem)) 0DF61E8B0B0302 /var>. Retournez vite auprès de Gullinkambi pour les lui apporter.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ725_01929_SEQ_03<tab>You return to Anyx Trine where Gullinkambi is salivating from the mere scent of the bandersnatch meat. She consumes it hungrily, thanking you in between bites. With a quieted belly, she can continue guarding her eggs with peace of mind.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ725_01929_SEQ_03<tab>De retour à Annexe Trine, vous avez remis la viande de bandersnatch à Gullinkambi. Salivant à l'idée de s'en repaître, la dragonne vous a remercié<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var> pour votre généreuse action.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ725_01929_TODO_00<tab>Slay golden bandersnatches for their meat.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ725_01929_TODO_00<tab>Tuez des bandersnatchs dorés pour obtenir leur viande

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ725_01929_TODO_01<tab>Deliver the bandersnatch meat to Gullinkambi.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ725_01929_TODO_01<tab>Apporter la viande de bandersnatch à Gullinkambi

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ725_01929_GULLINKAMBI_000_000<tab>My stomach roils, it longs for sustenance. I must feed to maintain my strength and guard these eggs.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ725_01929_GULLINKAMBI_000_000<tab>Mon estomac n'en finit plus de gronder. Je dois me nourrir pour reprendre des forces et garder mes œufs.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ725_01929_GULLINKAMBI_000_001<tab>Only the most succulent of meats can satisfy my cravings. I must have the bandersnatch. Bring me three chunks of their flesh from the cave near the Iron Feast.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ725_01929_GULLINKAMBI_000_001<tab>Seule la meilleure des viandes peut me satisfaire... Comme celle des bandersnatchs dorés de cette grotte, aux Cent Râles. Apporte-m'en trois morceaux.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ725_01929_GULLINKAMBI_000_010<tab>Too long has it been since I feasted on the bandersnatch. No less than three chunks of their flesh will fill my belly.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ725_01929_GULLINKAMBI_000_010<tab>Il y a bien trop longtemps que je n'ai pas dégusté cette délicieuse viande de bandersnatch... Apporte-m'en trois morceaux de cette grotte, aux Cent Râles.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ725_01929_GULLINKAMBI_000_020<tab><sniff> <sniff> That savor... Give it to me. I must have it.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ725_01929_GULLINKAMBI_000_020<tab>Ce délicieux parfum... Vite, montre-moi la viande.

source: TEXT_HEAVNZ725_01929_GULLINKAMBI_000_021<tab><gulp> Ah, yes, there is no flesh better than that of bandersnatch. Thank you. The solitude of this tower can prove vexing, but a sated stomach makes my duties more bearable.
target: TEXT_HEAVNZ725_01929_GULLINKAMBI_000_021<tab>Ah, je reconnais bien la délicieuse chair de bandersnatch. Merci, humain<var 08 E905 ((e)) (()) /var>. Cette solitude me pèse, mais ma tâche me semblera plus plaisante l'estomac bien rempli.
